      "content": "Interesting. You mentioned that the \"changing demographics\" in Profile B pose a risk because of the \"influx of new, often lower-income residents.\" \n\nCan you elaborate on why a shift in the racial or ethnic makeup of a neighborhood is typically treated as a risk factor for property value stability? Is there a direct correlation between demographic diversity and market volatility?",
